Invocation Name: unofficial disney guessing game
des:
Who's That Disney Character (Unofficial) is a question and answer trivia game. You'll be asked to identify the Disney character based on their silhouette (on Echo Show and Echo Spot devices) and their description.

You can say, "I don't know" to hear the correct answer, or "Skip" to move on to the next Disney character. You can say "Repeat" to hear the description again.

For the full experience, try Who's That Disney Character (Unofficial) on a device with a screen, where you'll see the blacked-out image of the Disney character!
